**Education loans** in India cover tuition fees, hostel, books, and other study expenses. Interest rates range from 8.85% p.a. (for Premier Institute categories) to 14% for private lenders. The loan has a moratorium period (study duration + 6–12 months) during which you pay only simple interest. Section 80E provides a tax deduction on interest paid for 8 years.
